<DocsLayout title="For Service Providers" section="Notifications">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Set up text and email notifications to keep technicians informed about their
    dispatched visits, reminders, and any schedule changes.
  </p>
  <p>
    Technicians can get caught up in their current tasks and forget about their next
    appointment. Notifications ensure they arrive on time, maintaining quality service
    and keeping dispatch on track.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Access</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Text Messages:</strong> Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Company</strong> → <strong>Text Message Settings</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Email Notifications:</strong> Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Company</strong> → <strong>Manage Users</strong></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Text Message Notifications</h2>
  <img src="/images/notifications/notificationforcustomers_02.webp" alt="Text Notifications" />

  <h3>Available Notifications</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Scheduled Visit:</strong> Notify technicians when a visit has been dispatched to them</li>
    <li><strong>Reminder:</strong> Send reminders about upcoming dispatched visits</li>
    <li><strong>Schedule Changes:</strong> Notify when a dispatch has been modified</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Email Notifications</h2>

  <h3>Available Notifications</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Schedule Assigned:</strong> Notify via email when a visit is assigned</li>
    <li><strong>Schedule Changes:</strong> Notify via email when a visit is modified</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Per-User Settings</h2>
  <img src="/images/notifications/notificationforcustomers_01.webp" alt="User Settings" />
  <p>
    Text and email notifications can be configured at the service provider level,
    allowing customized communication with each technician based on their preferences.
  </p>

  <h2>Notifications & Permissions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Notification settings can be customized per technician</li>
    <li>Administrators configure which notifications each technician receives</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <div class="callout callout-tip">
    <p>
      <strong>Set up timely reminders</strong> — technicians focused on one job may forget about the next dispatched job.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Enable schedule change notifications</strong> to keep technicians informed of updates.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Use both text and email</strong> for redundancy on important notifications.
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
